  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT MODALITY - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
The type of treatment delivered as part of a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_radiotherapy_prescription">RADIOTHERAPY PRESCRIPTION</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
Where the treatment is delivered as part of a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_cancer_treatment_period">Cancer Treatment Period</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_radiotherapy_treatment_modality">RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>
 is equivalent to 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_cancer_treatment_modality">CANCER TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>
 National Codes 
              <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_teletherapy">Teletherapy</xref>'</i>
 or 
              <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_brachytherapy">Brachytherapy</xref>'</i>.         </p>
  </div>
